<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The section of the Spreadsheets documentation on editing rows (currently section 16.6.4.5: "Edit a Row") only mentions how to use Zend_Gdata_Spreadsheets::updateRow() to update cells in a spreadsheet.</p>

<p>However, updateRow() can be inconvenient, as all old data in the updated row will be obliterated. A common use case is to update only a small subset of the data in a row. To accommodate this, this section of the manual should be expanded to demonstrate using of Zend_Gdata_Spreadsheets_ListEntry::getCustomByName() to edit individual cells.</p>

